                            <comment id="17057889" author="mxm" created="Thu, 12 Mar 2020 12:39:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Should add that this eventually causes the meta space to run out after many job restarts because the lingering threads prevent old classloaders from becoming garbage collected.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
